text: Arnold Thomsen (31 May 1913 - 8 June 2001) was a Danish gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1948 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1913 births Category:2001 deaths Category:Danish male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Denmark Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:People from Esbjerg
